{"word":"G4084 - πιάζω - piázō - pee-ad'-zo - Apprehend","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πιάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">piázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pee-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Apprehend</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிடி, பிடித்துக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to lay hold of"},{"paragraph":"2. to take, capture"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably another form of <a href=\"#/G971 - βιάζω - biázō - bee-ad'-zo/971\">G971</a>; to <i>squeeze</i>, that is, <i>seize</i> (gently by the hand [<i>press</i>], or officially [<i>arrest</i>], or in hunting [<i>capture</i>]): - apprehend, catch, lay hand on, take. Compare <a href=\"#/G4085 - πιέζω - piézō - pee-ed'-zo/4085\">G4085</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}